Package org.cyclops.cyclopscore.recipe.custom

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Recipe<I extends IRecipeInput,O extends IRecipeOutput,P extends IRecipeProperties>
    Basic recipe that can be registered with SuperRecipeRegistry.
    RecipeHandlerMachine<M extends IMachine<M,I,O,P>,I extends IRecipeInput,O extends IRecipeOutput,P extends IRecipeProperties>
    An adapter class for exposing an IMachine as an IRecipeHandler.
    RecipeMatch<M extends IMachine,R extends IRecipe>
    A match for a recipe, holds the recipe and the machine it is associated with.
    RecipeMatcher<M extends IMachine,R extends IRecipe>
    Helper class to abstract away some function logic (lambdas would make this way simpler though).
    RecipePropertyMatcher<M extends IMachine,R extends IRecipe,P>
    It allows you to match a property of a recipe to the properties of all other registered recipes and return any recipes whose properties match.
    RecipeRegistry<M extends IMachine<M,I,O,P>,I extends IRecipeInput,O extends IRecipeOutput,P extends IRecipeProperties>
    Default implementation of IRecipeRegistry.
    SuperRecipeRegistry
    This class allows you to register new recipes for machines.
